                "The relative Cd-yield data were normalized to mass=111.",
                " The yield of mass=113 was established by smooth",
                " extrapolation of the curve through masses 111 and 112.",
                " Then the yield of mass=114 was obtained by subtraction",
                " of the 113-yield from the normalized measured sum of",
                " relative abundances of masses 113+114.",
                " The tin-yields were matched to normalized Cd-yields",
